	xen "drbd" vbd type implementation
drbd.sh.rhcs
	resource script for Red Hat Cluster Suite rgmanager
drbd.metadata.rhcs
	resource script metadata for Red Hat Cluster Suite rgmanager
outdate-peer.sh
	example implementation of the fence-peer mechanism using ssh
drbd.conf
	commented example configuration
drbd-overview.pl
	consolidates /proc/drbd, /etc/drbd.conf, xm list, lvs, df
pretty-proc-drbd.sh
	example how to pretty-print (optionally with color) /proc/drbd

